WEBVTT

00:01.787 --> 00:04.536
I can't believe you guys
are still staring over there.

00:04.787 --> 00:07.536
Some mothers tend to breast-feed
for a lot longer these days.

00:07.537 --> 00:09.906
It's called detachment parenting.

00:11.637 --> 00:13.906
When the kid is that big,
it's called dating.

00:16.036 --> 00:18.906
I mean, he's gotta come up
for air at some point.

00:18.908 --> 00:22.176
No, he doesn't.

00:22.178 --> 00:23.911
Isn't he too old
to drink from the teat?

00:23.913 --> 00:25.450
The kid
is my height.

00:29.852 --> 00:32.853
Don't get any ideas.

00:32.855 --> 00:37.558
Well, it's happened:
I've lived too long.

00:37.560 --> 00:39.226
I'm ready to order.

00:39.228 --> 00:41.061
I can't.
I mean, I respect it all,

00:41.063 --> 00:43.464
but I'll throw up.

00:43.466 --> 00:45.432
I'll go.
I can't afford HBO,

00:45.434 --> 00:51.238
and it's the closest I can get
to seeing <i>Game of Thrones.</i>

00:51.240 --> 00:52.540
Hi, what can I get you?

00:52.542 --> 00:55.843
He's obviously good drink-wise.

00:55.845 --> 00:57.545
I'll have tea
and a turkey club.

00:57.547 --> 01:01.248
Anything for him?
Coffee for the milk?

01:01.250 --> 01:03.450
Burger? Fries?

01:03.452 --> 01:05.786
I'll have fries.

